As we can see above, each of the cases of hypertension for males and females were calculated separately.

we divided cases for each sex by total Persons in each sex for calculate infection rate for each sex without being affected by the number of people, and the equation would be balanced.

According to the results shown above, the rate of women suffering from hypertension is higher than men.

print("Alcoholism No Show Percentage is",Alcoholism_No_Show,"% and No Alcoholism No Show Percentage is",No_Alcoholism_No_Show,"%")

Alcoholism No Show Percentage is 23 % and No Alcoholism No Show Percentage is 19 %

According to the results shown above, alcohol addiction affects attendance on time. The percentage of addicts who do not attend is greater than those who do not attend and are not alcoholics.
